import{menuTL}from"./menuAnimation";import{gsap}from"gsap/all";import{ScrollToPlugin}from"gsap/ScrollToPlugin";gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollToPlugin);export function scrolltoProjects(){let e=document.querySelector("#hscroll");const t=window.matchMedia("(min-width: 992px)");document.querySelectorAll("#navmenu a").forEach((o=>{o.addEventListener("click",(function(o){o.preventDefault();const n=this.getAttribute("href").split("#")[1],r=document.getElementById(n);document.getElementById("masthead");t.matches?(gsap.to(window,{scrollTo:r.offsetLeft*(e.offsetWidth/(e.offsetWidth-r.offsetWidth)),duration:.5}),menuTL.reverse()):(gsap.to(window,{scrollTo:r,duration:.5}),menuTL.reverse())}))}))}